  "description": "Adds in many cool new dishes with special features.",
  "body": "<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Delicious Dishes is a minecraft food overhaul mod.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">It adds many cool new 3D modeled meals that can be eaten multiple times, just like cake.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">To view the recipes use either the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/patchouli\">Patchouli</a> guide that can be found in village chests or <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/roughly-enough-items\">RoughlyEnoughItems</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod was originally made for modfest 1.16.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vP9m5xC/dishes-ps.png\" width=\"1167\" height=\"152\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/Motschen/Assets/blob/main/quilt+fabric-banner.png?raw=true\" height=\"56\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HQdFUUqLF3c?wmode=transparent\" height=\"358\" width=\"638\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/XJwM0qB/abetterplace.png\" width=\"992\" height=\"216\" /></p>",
